CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)

NEW DELIHI, the 19th February,1986
.... •
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from
19th February, 1986, Shri Ajit Panja, Minister of State in the Ministry
of Planning will also be temporarily Minister of State in the Ministry
of Food and Civil Supplies under Shri P. Shiv Shapkar, Minister of
Commerce and Food and Civil Supplies.
( H.R. GOEL)
for CABINET SECRETARY
